						<div class="postbody">Another advantage to 2x2 meta tiles is that collision detection is SO much easier, since there aren't more than $FF meta tiles on screen at once. You can read the bytes of maps easier, you can just read map,x to read any tile on the screen, due to there only being $FF tiles. This is why making my <a href="http://www.freewebs.com/the_bott/cynthi.nes" class="postlink">NES meta tile layer</a> was so easy to do.</div>

					
